'''Ryan Church''' is a Concept Design Supervisor at [[Lucasfilm]]. He has been behind many of the concepts shown on [[StarWars.com]]'s [[Art of Revenge]], and is known for his vehicle designs, upon which many of the vehicles in the latter two episodes of the [[prequel trilogy]] are based.

==Biography==
[[File:Ryan002_bg.jpg|thumb|left|Church at Skywalker Ranch.]]
Ryan Church joined [[Industrial Light & Magic]] in the [[Lucasfilm Animation|digital feature division]] in 1998. Shortly after the release of [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''The Phantom Menace'']], he moved onto JAK Films, where he served as a Concept Design Supervisor on [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Episode II'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Episode III'']], and a Senior Art Director in their post-productions.

In 2013, Church returned to ILM and worked on [[Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens|''Star Wars'': Episode VII ''The Force Awakens'']], ''[[Rogue One: A Star Wars Story]]'' and ''[[Star Wars: The Mandalorian]].''

==Original designs==
[[File:Fedspheretroops.jpg|thumb|right|250px|Episode II concept art by Church depicting the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|First Battle of Geonosis]].]]
Ryan Church influenced the design of many of the worlds in Episodes II and III. Although he specializes in futuristic vehicles and spacecraft, his contributions run the spectrum of design, from planets to characters:
*[[All Terrain Tactical Enforcer/Legends|AT-TE]]
*[[IG-227 Hailfire-class droid tank/Legends|Hailfire droid tank]]
*[[NR-N99 Persuader-class droid enforcer/Legends|Corporate Alliance tank droid]]
[[File:Carrierbattle.jpg|thumb|right|250px|[[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|Episode III]] concept art by Church depicting a [[Venator-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Venator''-class Star Destroyer]] disgorging fighters over [[Cato Neimoidia/Legends|Cato Neimoidia]].]]
*[[Aggressive ReConnaissance-170 starfighter/Legends|ARC-170]]
*[[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]] (Episode III appearance)
*[[Tantive IV/Legends|Tantive IV]] (Episode III variation)
*[[Mygeeto/Legends|Mygeeto]]
*[[Felucia/Legends|Felucia]]
*[[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] (Episode III appearance)
*[[Polis Massa/Legends|Polis Massa]]
*[[LM-432 crab droid/Legends|Crab droid]]
*[[Pistoeka sabotage droid/Legends|Buzz droid]]
*[[Octuptarra combat tri-droid/Legends|Octuptarra combat tri-droid]]
*[[Octuptarra magna tri-droid/Legends|Octuptarra magna tri-droid]]

